import React from 'react'; import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableHead, TableRow } from '@mui/material'; import '../components/ReportsTable.css' const ReportsTable = ({ reports }) => { return ( ID Test Version Build Cluster Result Failure Reason Runtime Date User {reports.map((report) => ( {report.id} {report.test} {report.versionBuild} {report.cluster} {report.result} {report.failureReason} {report.runtime} {report.date} {report.user} ))}
); }; export default ReportsTable;
